                            <comment id="12680960" author="eamonndwyer" created="Wed, 11 Mar 2009 18:11:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch attached is a possible solution to this issue&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12680961" author="eamonndwyer" created="Wed, 11 Mar 2009 18:12:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I should add I spotted this while using the &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/cxf/branches/2.0.x-fixes&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/cxf/branches/2.0.x-fixes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
branch so the fix could be applied just there. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12680973" author="dkulp" created="Wed, 11 Mar 2009 18:37:53 +0000"  >
&lt;p&gt;Actually, the fix is even easier:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;listeners = new ArrayList&amp;lt;BusLifeCycleListener&amp;gt;();&lt;br/&gt;
+        listeners = new CopyOnWriteArrayList&amp;lt;BusLifeCycleListener&amp;gt;();&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Anyway, I&apos;ll get the committed and merged down.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
